definitions.definition: ( British , Ireland , Australia , South Africa , New Zealand ) An absorbent garment worn by a baby or toddler who does not yet have voluntary control of their bladder and bowels or by someone who is incontinent ; a diaper .

main_definition: ( British , Ireland , Australia , South Africa , New Zealand ) An absorbent garment worn by a baby or toddler who does not yet have voluntary control of their bladder and bowels or by someone who is incontinent ; a diaper .

definitions.definition: A shallow, flat-bottomed earthenware or glass bowl with sloping sides.

main_definition: A shallow, flat-bottomed earthenware or glass bowl with sloping sides.

definitions.definition: A kind of strong ale ; nappy ale .

main_definition: ( obsolete ) A kind of strong ale ; nappy ale .
